L.M., Petitioner,
v.
Laura HAMILTON, et al., Respondents. No. 95173-0 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, September 6, 2018

ORDER

¶ 1 This matter came before the Court on its September 6, 2018, En Banc Conference. The Court considered the petition and the files herein. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is granted. Any party may serve and file a supplemental brief within 30 days of the date of this order, see RAP 13.7(d).

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J. CHIEF JUSTICE
